properties.Name: EquifaxCompanyPublicRecordsSummary
properties.Description: A summary of the Equifax company's public records.

Columns.Name: EfxId
Columns.Description: The EFX ID™ is a unique and persistent nine-digit number that identifies and tracks the business unit with which you have the credit relationship;

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description:
Provides the timestamp when the inquiry was made as recorded
by Equifax (Eastern Time).

Columns.Name: BankruptciesMostRecentDateFiled
Columns.Description: The date that the most recent bankruptcy was filed.

Columns.Name: BankruptciesAmount
Columns.Description: The amount associated with reported bankruptcies.

Columns.Name: JudgmentsMostRecentDateFiled
Columns.Description: The date that the most recent judgment was filed.

Columns.Name: JudgmentsSatisfiedMostRecentDateFiled
Columns.Description: The date that the most recent satisfied judgment was filed.

Columns.Name: LiensMostRecentDateFiled
Columns.Description: The date that the most recent liens was filed.

Columns.Name: MostRecentSatisfiedLiensDateFiled
Columns.Description: The date that the most recent satisfied liens were filed.
